17:59.045 --> 18:01.181
- Dr. Charles--sorry.

18:01.181 --> 18:04.217
I just wanted to let you know
that Jessica Pope...

18:04.217 --> 18:05.752
she didn't make it.

18:06.886 --> 18:10.490
- Thank you.
- Yeah.

18:17.730 --> 18:20.233
- The thing about psychopaths...

18:22.569 --> 18:25.605
Love to hear themselves talk.

18:33.713 --> 18:35.415
- Yeah?
- We picked up footage

18:35.415 --> 18:37.717
of your car outside Callie's
house the night of the incident.

18:37.717 --> 18:39.519
- You mean the night
your partner killed my brother.

18:39.519 --> 18:41.354
- Yeah, and I know
you drove him there.

18:41.354 --> 18:43.190
- So?
