- Exactly.

20:08.941 --> 20:11.478
- Did they cure cancer?
[laughs]

20:11.478 --> 20:13.946
That shuts 'em up.

20:13.946 --> 20:16.115
You know, bottom line,

20:16.115 --> 20:17.784
