20:29.228 --> 20:30.563
Yeah, I got a guy,

20:30.563 --> 20:33.800
uh, Howard, on South Wabash.

20:33.800 --> 20:36.168
This retails 75,000 easy.

20:36.168 --> 20:37.704
He gave it to me for 45,000.

20:37.704 --> 20:39.706
- Whew.
- [chuckles]

20:39.706 --> 20:42.241
If you're interested I can,
uh, give you his info.

20:42.241 --> 20:44.377
He can hook you up.
I mean, look at this thing.

20:44.377 --> 20:47.914
- Wow, gorgeous.

20:47.914 --> 20:50.783
Really gorgeous.
- Yeah.

20:50.783 --> 20:53.786
